{"tid":838844,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］秋季水果真係好好好好食","createTime":"2018-09-27T12:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T07:23:38.000Z","uid":150912,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a24081079d33117f2ffbc150c4354c8c4716382f","tid":838844,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"楊桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好食黃色果d 因為咁先夠熟<br />\n甜得黎極多汁<br />\n好耐冇俾水果口爆過<br />\nD水係儲係d果肉到 唔同西瓜咁散<br />\n一咬入去就好似醬爆瀨尿牛丸咁噴出黎<br />\n果種清涼同甜爽的感覺係冇水果比得上<br />\n食的方法研究過  最好係打橫切3-4份<br />\n保留星形狀<br />\n千期唔好切5角搞到好似人柱咁 <br />\n因為中間最多水  <br />\n之後一野啪入口 （預備紙巾）<br />\n俾d汁爆出黎  啜乾d水食埋d肉<br />\n最後先慢慢吐返中間條芯同核<br />\n包你一試上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次係爽柿<br />\n爽柿要買d表面有少少漏糖的<br />\n太生會澀<br />\n批左皮切開4-6等份就啪得<br />\n食落似咬口似美國熟桃  但完全冇桃的酸  係連少少酸都唔會有  <br />\n肉的組織密實  唔似一般桃食完有空虛感<br />\n非常滿足<br />\n又潤又甜<br />\n加上D核軟軟爽爽又多汁  <br />\n一啖接一啖 好快就食完一個  忍唔住要開多個黎食<br />\n<br />\n最後係林柿<br />\n林柿唔擺得<br />\n買左最好2日內食 否則芯易變黑<br />\n而靚的林柿就好似蜜糖做的軟膏咁樣<br />\n啖啖都係漏糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n滋潤又清甜<br />\n剝完皮將林柿切開2-3份左右  <br />\n隊埋嘴邊啜佢一啖甜肉 <br />\nd肉一滑入口<br />\n就好似俾林柿反客為主佔據左  非常滋潤<br />\n然後再啪埋另一半入口<br />\n慢慢啜佢d肉  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  等d肉滑入喉嚨<br />\n最後啜剩個晶瑩剔透的核 <br />\n之後先一野咬爆佢  感受埋最後一陣的甜同成個林柿中唯一的爽脆<br />\n好食到升仙<br />\n<br />\n之後係碌柚<br />\n其實我唔係特別鍾意食碌柚<br />\n所以算啦<br />\n甜的都好食既<br />\n是但啦<br />\n<br />\n總結：秋季水果好撚正<br />\n各位巴打把握時間快d食<br />\n過左就要等下年架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a098a2cf764ceda91ee6af55b463f8cb30d94c4","tid":838844,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b372f77775510fec18c0c2dfa47ff4284a6c3c","tid":838844,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55410c3db0ce5c4c5e2449eae2dd746cdc2740fe","tid":838844,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"春夏秋冬嘅生果都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7925503fb9d9799baf58b64dccfb2d7b7807d9da","tid":838844,"uid":194368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"梨都好食, 反而柿好少食"},{"pid":"0a6d2d42fdbfcd472ed4e6df52d721896e51073e","tid":838844,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7925503fb9d9799baf58b64dccfb2d7b7807d9da","tid":838844,"uid":194368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"梨都好食, 反而柿好少食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"但係梨一年四季都有"},{"pid":"2396e6eb93c5fc674fba22e2a7254a66d433949b","tid":838844,"uid":144156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"碌柚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日一粒"},{"pid":"45941d8d12bf20c29abdadf05a57e3d8209094ed","tid":838844,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"Royal 級？"},{"pid":"94ea293dfba55afd06459232b97df8624c99483f","tid":838844,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"文旦最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}